OL,3,CBaggage screeners at Gatwick Airport
OL,4,Ccall off strike action after new pay
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FPlanned strike action by baggage
OL,8,Fscreeners at Gatwick Airport has been
OL,9,Fcancelled after the workers accepted a
OL,10,Fnew pay deal, a union has said.
OL,12,FUnite baggage workers, employed by
OL,13,FICTS, had scheduled strike action from
OL,14,F29 August to 2 September.
OL,16,FThe strikes were suspended when the
OL,17,Fcompany returned with an improved
OL,18,Foffer for the workers to consider.
