OL,4,Ccall off strike action after new pay
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FThe baggage screeners will now receive
OL,8,Fa 7% increase in hourly pay, backdated
OL,9,Fto April 2025, along with other
OL,10,Fimproved benefits.
OL,12,FThe union has said the workers were
OL,13,Famong the lowest paid at the West
OL,14,FSussex airport, earning 'just above
OL,15,Fthe minimum wage'.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, ICTS made a profit before
OL,18,Ftax of #6.1 million in 2024, a 46.9%
OL,19,Fincrease compared to the previous
OL,20,Fyear, according to the union.
