OL,7,FA spokesperson for Gatwick Airport
OL,8,Fsaid on X, they were 'pleased' the
OL,9,Faction had been called off and are
OL,10,Flooking forward to welcoming
OL,11,Fpassengers 'as normal' over the coming
OL,12,Fdays.
OL,14,FDuring the dispute, Unite said 'all
OL,15,Fflights' out of Gatwick would face
OL,16,Fdisruption and threatened that
OL,17,Findustrial action would 'intensify' if
OL,18,Fit was not resolved.
